text: "Parallel Line" is a 2018 song by country singer Keith Urban and is the second single from his 10th studio album Graffiti U. It went to number 78 in Scotland, number 47 in Australia and number 25 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart. It contains a sample of the 2014 song Everglow by Coldplay. ==References== Category:2018 songs Category:Country pop songs Category:Keith Urban songs
